! Universal X resources (all machines). Keep host-independent settings ONLY.
! Display-dependent knobs (Xft.dpi, Xcursor.size) live in per-host overlays
! named .Xresources.$(hostname) (e.g. .Xresources.popos), merged after this
! file by i3/.config/i3/xsettings.sh — same per-host pattern as
! i3/.config/i3/display_setup.sh.
